---
import Card from "../Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-2 lg:row-span-6 " title="">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-2xl">
    <div class="text-base font-light h-fit">
      <p>
        I am Enoch, a data enthusiast from the <a class="text-red-400 capitalize italic font-semibold" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Little_red_dot" aria-label="Little Red Dot">little red dot 🔴</a>.
        <br />
        I love analysing trends and making predictions using machine learning!
        <br />
    </div>
    <p class="text-base ">
      I have built Telegram bots, upgraded PCs and laptops, and set up a home lab for ad-blocking and media sharing!
      <br />
    </p>
    <p class="text-base font-light">
      Outside of coding, I am either playing with my cat 🐱, training/coaching ultimate frisbee 🥏 or just enjoying a cup of coffee ☕️. 
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
